      {
         "id": "update",
         "desc": "",
         "target": "",
         "page": "",
         "value_type": "",
         "html_value": "<p><h3>Updates and Navigation</h3><b>Some previously published family records have been temporarily hidden pending the completion of the standardization process. However, they remain accessible in the project's GitHub repository (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('68c5b4fe-6794-461d-b3e6-40cf62d4b7a4'); return false;\">History Tracers, Github</a>).</b></p><p><b>Family records may be updated at any time based on new research. <span id=\"family_common_sn\"></span></b></p><p>The calendars currently in use were not always the same as those referenced in historical documentation. In the prerequisites section of each family record, we specify the calendars used in their respective documentation.</p><p>Whenever you access a family page, you will find a <b>Prerequisites Section</b> at the top, highlighting essential texts for understanding that family's history.</p><h3>Genealogical Tree</h3>",
         "value": null,
         "date_time": null
